CanvasApp.Name: cr382_refundvalidator_68109
CanvasApp.Description:
Validate refund requests submitted by collaborators.
This app allows finance or administrative teams to review, approve, or reject expense refund requests submitted by staff members. Each request includes relevant details such as the collaborator’s name, description, amount, attached receipts, and status.
Key Features:
Review attached files (receipts or documents)
Approve or reject requests with comments
Automatically mark as "Refunded" upon approval
Track request history and status changes
Assign reimbursement status and export for records
Designed to streamline the reimbursement workflow and maintain accountability in financial operations.
